Path: godot/classes/class_dpitexture.rst
Summary: DPITexture is a texture that can store multiple resolutions of the same image.

DPITexture is a texture that can store multiple resolutions of the same image. This allows for more efficient rendering on different screen densities, as the appropriate resolution can be chosen based on the device's DPI.

Inherits: Texture2D < Texture < Resource < RefCounted
