Document: DPITexture
Path: godot/classes/class_dpitexture.rst
Summary: Describes the DPITexture class, which provides a scalable Texture2D based on an SVG image for UI elements.
DPITexture is an automatically scalable Texture2D based on an SVG image. DPITexture s are used to automatically re-rasterize icons and other texture based UI theme elements to match viewport scale and font oversampling. See also ProjectSettings.display/window/stretch/mode ("canvas_items" mode) and Viewport.oversampling_override.
